              </p>
              <button onClick={() => setActiveTab('curso')} className="px-12 py-5 rounded-2xl bg-white text-gray-500 font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-all flex items-center gap-3">Começar Agora <ArrowRight size={20}/></button>
